post.body: Just found Zeronet last night. Did some reading on it... I gotta say this seems like the best thing to happen to the internet since google!! Completely anonymous, blockchain based, borderless, and only accessible through zeronet similar to .onion through tor!! already has built in site and creating a new site is simple copy paste codes... I look forward to being able to use this to finally be free to be myself!!
